Subject: [PATCH] 8997: V850: Add p-code emulation test classes

#8998 V850: Add p-code emulation test classes

Add EmulatorTest JUnit classes for the V850 processor module and the
Base dependency needed for ProcessorEmulatorTestAdapter.

Enables `gradle :V850:pcodeTest` once pcodetest binaries are built
via the SleighDevTools build system (`python3 pcodetest.py -t V850`).

- Add V850_O0_EmulatorTest.java and V850_O3_EmulatorTest.java
- Add Base dependency to build.gradle for test compilation
---
 Ghidra/Processors/V850/build.gradle           |  4 ++
 .../test/processors/V850_O0_EmulatorTest.java | 40 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../test/processors/V850_O3_EmulatorTest.java | 40 +++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 84 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 Ghidra/Processors/V850/src/test.processors/java/ghidra/test/processors/V850_O0_EmulatorTest.java
 create mode 100644 Ghidra/Processors/V850/src/test.processors/java/ghidra/test/processors/V850_O3_EmulatorTest.java

diff --git a/Ghidra/Processors/V850/build.gradle b/Ghidra/Processors/V850/build.gradle
index b5b745ae39..bf603fd0fe 100644
--- a/Ghidra/Processors/V850/build.gradle
+++ b/Ghidra/Processors/V850/build.gradle
@@ -20,3 +20,7 @@ apply from: "$rootProject.projectDir/gradle/jacocoProject.gradle"
 apply from: "$rootProject.projectDir/gradle/javaTestProject.gradle"
 apply plugin: 'eclipse'
 eclipse.project.name = 'Processors v850'
+
+dependencies {
+	api project(':Base')
+}
diff --git a/Ghidra/Processors/V850/src/test.processors/java/ghidra/test/processors/V850_O0_EmulatorTest.java b/Ghidra/Processors/V850/src/test.processors/java/ghidra/test/processors/V850_O0_EmulatorTest.java
